# Entites
entity.shadowmobs.phantom.name=Phantom
entity.shadowmobs.phantom.description=Wrathful death entities with a thirst for souls! Phantoms are attracted to death and sometimes mistake people who are asleep as dead! Their ranged attacks cause their victims to run around fear!
achievement.phantom.kill=Reaping The Reaper!
achievement.phantom.kill.desc=Slay a Phantom.
achievement.phantom.learn=Deaths Hand
achievement.phantom.learn.desc=Add a Phantom to your Beastiary.
achievement.phantom.summon=Fear Me!
achievement.phantom.summon.desc=Summon a Phantom.
entity.shadowmobs.epion.name=Epion
entity.shadowmobs.epion.description=Giant shadow blood bats! Epions spit Bloodleeches at their victims, draining health on hit. When in contact with the sun, Epions drop to the ground and explode on impact!
achievement.epion.kill=Lunar Leechers!
achievement.epion.kill.desc=Slay an Epion.
achievement.epion.learn=Explosive In Sunlight!
achievement.epion.learn.desc=Add an Epion to your Beastiary.
entity.shadowmobs.geist.name=Geist
entity.shadowmobs.geist.description=Geists are opportunistic creatures that deform and climb into undead lifeforms and feed off whatever their host is capable of killing. When their host dies, Geists leap out and reform for a surprise attack!
achievement.geist.kill=Shadowfire Everywhere!
achievement.geist.kill.desc=Slay a Geist.
achievement.geist.learn=They Haunt The Undead!
achievement.geist.learn.desc=Add a Geist to your Beastiary.
entity.shadowmobs.chupacabra.name=Chupacabra
entity.shadowmobs.chupacabra.description=Dreadful creatures that lurk within the darkest caverns beneath the earth, their insatiable hunger for flesh can be used to manipulate and farm them. Their bite is not only fatal but heals them.
achievement.chupacabra.kill=Shadow Hunters!
achievement.chupacabra.kill.desc=Slay a Chupacabra.
achievement.chupacabra.learn=Chupacabra... Farming?
achievement.chupacabra.learn.desc=Add a Chupacabra to your Beastiary.
achievement.chupacabra.tame=Aww! Rub its belly!
achievement.chupacabra.tame.desc=Tame a Chupacabra.
entity.shadowmobs.shade.name=Shade
entity.shadowmobs.shade.description=Wicked embodiments of deadly shadow magic. Shades are large, fast and deadly. Their attacks drain a bit of health and they have a horrific howl sending all that oppose them running in fear!
achievement.shade.kill=Smite Meister!
achievement.shade.kill.desc=Slay a Shade.
achievement.shade.learn=Darkness Incarnate!
achievement.shade.learn.desc=Add a Shade to your Beastiary.
achievement.shade.tame=Horrific Howl!
achievement.shade.tame.desc=Tame a Shade.
entity.shadowmobs.darkling.name=Darkling
entity.shadowmobs.darkling.description=Foul little shadow insects that like to latch onto their victim and slowly drain their blood, feasting to regain any lost health! You best swat these pests off fast!
achievement.darkling.kill=Get Off Me!
achievement.darkling.kill.desc=Slay a Darkling.
achievement.darkling.learn=Worse Than Lice!
achievement.darkling.learn.desc=Add a Darkling to your Beastiary.
achievement.darkling.summon=Feed My Children!
achievement.darkling.summon.desc=Summon a Darkling.
